NeuralNetwork - Class in reactiveLayer
A class to model a topologically-organised lattice of neurons, resembling a 2D grid of neurons that are connected to each neuron in its Moore neighbourhood (its surrounding eight neurons).
NeuralNetwork(int, int) - Constructor for class reactiveLayer.NeuralNetwork
Creates a topologically-organised lattice of neurons in a rows x cols grid.
Neuron - Class in reactiveLayer
A class to model a Neuron with a location, which holds the neurons it is neighbours to, and has an activation value.
